      <title>法国电网负责人称可再生能源必须帮助平衡电网</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/renewables-must-help-balance-power-network-french-grid-boss-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国电网负责人表示，如果可再生能源要继续快速扩张，风能和太阳能发电场将必须像其他发电机一样全面参与平衡电网。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/renewables-must-help-balance-power-network-french-grid-boss-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 15:34:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
